sentences: They released their first EP, The Other Side of You in February 2011.
They released their first album, Backbone, in 2012.
In 2014, they were among the Top 3 of the New Music Seminar Artist on the Verge Top 100.
In 2016, Melissa Menago released her first solo album, Little Crimes, on Chesky Records.
In 2016, June Divided released their third album, Body Wars, featuring Menago as lead vocals, guitar and keyboard.
Melissa Menago is an American singer and songwriter who sings lead vocals for the band June Divided.
In 2020, June Divided released the single "The Wall".
